  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He say, yes, I am 26.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "After the marriage, they found out they not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Anyway, so Daddy told him, I'm going back home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That's how he left the tie there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I'm going back home, you know, we left [INAUDIBLE], Mom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And whoever thought of something horrifying, such an annihilation to the Jewish culture and people, and-- and complete to wipe off something which we never in the world's history ever happened.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This kind of-- and this is the 20th century, the civilization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I think, this is civilization, I think that the people have a lot to learn yet, if this-- that could something happen like this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we didn't, he didn't, nobody expects this kind of tragedy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when Daddy came back, and my daddy told my brother, if it quiets down, don't forget to come back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a neighbor also, one of the youngest of the Schwartzbaum, or one of our tenants, what they didn't live with us, but I mean they had been friends before.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you come with him then, my brother promised.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Russia had a trick, and made a big announcement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who like to go home to register?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted to show off with his bride.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so they registered, and they sent them to Siberia as spies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you want to go home, you came from there, but otherwise you're not-- you're spying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So both your-- your brother Josef and his new wife?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my sister-in-law, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Siberia, to Irkutsk, [INAUDIBLE], was 60 below zero.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know then what happened, but Daddy went.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
